.Dd December 16, 2005 
.Dt TPMS 4
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm tpms
.Nd Apple trackpad mouse support
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Cd "tpms*     at uhidev?"
.Cd "wsmouse* at tpms? mux 0"
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
driver provides support for the trackpads
on new Apple PowerBooks and iBooks that are
not standard USB HID mice.
Access to the mouse is through the
.Xr wscons 4
driver.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr uhidev 4 ,
.Xr usb 4 ,
.Xr wsmouse 4
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
driver
appeared in
.Ox 3.9 .
